Ranger Help for: strike
=======================

SYNTAX:      strike <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to deliver an enhanced melee hit against a
target. Strike is the basic combat attack skill for Rangers, dealing
more damage than a standard attack. It works with any wielded weapon
and in any terrain. Strike is often the first attack skill a Ranger
learns and serves as the foundation for more advanced techniques like
gash, impale, and naturestrike.
